ét nào.\r\n\r\n[/accordion-item]\r\n\r\n[/accordion]\r\n\r\n[/tab]\r\n\r\n[/tabgroup]\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[/row]\r\n\r\n[/section]','Câu hỏi thường gặp','','publish','closed','closed','','cau-hoi-thuong-gap','','','2018-08-07 10:50:38','2018-08-07 03:50:38','',0,'http://congty1.khowebseotop.vn/?page_id=511',0,'page','',0),(544,3,'2018-08-07 10:50:52','2018-08-07 03:50:52','[section bg=\"195\" bg_size=\"original\" padding=\"0px\"]\r\n\r\n[gap]\r\n\r\n[row]\r\n\r\n[col span__sm=\"12\" align=\"center\" color=\"light\"]\r\n<h2>Câu hỏi thường gặp</h2>\r\nChúng tôi giúp bạn trả lời mọi câu hỏi của bạn. Hãy gõ vào dưới đây để tìm câu trả lời bạn cần\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[/row]\r\n\r\n[/section]\r\n[row]\r\n\r\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\" align=\"center\"]\r\n\r\n[ux_image id=\"547\" image_size=\"original\" width=\"27\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">HDSD Tem QR Code Chống Giả\r\n<a href=\"http://qrcode-solution.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/HDSD-Tem-QR-Code-chong-gia-pdf.pdf\">Xem</a> |<a href=\"#\"> Tải xuống</a></span></p>\r\n[/col]\r\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\" align=\"center\"]\r\n\r\n[ux_image id=\"547\" image_size=\"original\" width=\"27\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Hướng Dấn Quét Mã QR Code\r\n<a href=\"http://qrcode-solution.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/HDSD-Tem-QR-Code-chong-gia-pdf.pdf\">Xem</a> |<a href=\"#\"> Tải xuống</a></span></p>\r\n[/col]\r\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\" align=\"center\"]\r\n\r\n[ux_image id=\"547\" image_size=\"original\" width=\"27\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Hướng Dẫn Tạo QR Code\r\n<a href=\"http://qrcode-solution.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/HDSD-Tem-QR-Code-chong-gia-pdf.pdf\">Xem</a> |<a href=\"#\"> Tải xuống</a></span></p>\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[/row]','Tài liệu hướng dẫn','','publish','closed','closed','','tai-lieu-huong-dan','','','2018-08-07 10:55:44','2018-08-07 03:55:44','',0,'http://congty1.kh